OL,3,CThree men who raped woman on beach
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FThree men who raped a woman on
OL,7,FBrighton beach have been jailed.
OL,9,FIranian national Abdulla Ahmadi, 26,
OL,10,Fand Egyptian nationals Ibrahim
OL,11,FAlshafe, 25, and Karin Al-Danasurt,
OL,12,F20, targeted the woman in the early
OL,13,Fhours of October 4 last year.
OL,15,FAhmadi and Alshafe were each jailed
OL,16,Ffor 21 years while Al-Danasurt was
OL,17,Fconvicted of rape as a secondary party
OL,18,Ffor filming the attack and was jailed
OL,19,Ffor 18 years and six months.
OL,21,FMore to follow...
